{"tid":780934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶驚見「一次性包皮環切器」！","createTime":"2018-08-15T13:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T16:08:50.000Z","uid":35814,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"37834ab468a90e42c6e6afa0cec44b9f22f6523b","tid":780934,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/37736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F37736&d=M8G5bui%2BjxuA9%2FsWM%2F8cFtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9bfd3862\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/37736</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都說網路上什麼都有、什麼都賣，幾乎可以說是只有醫療用品會受到管制，一般人不能隨意販賣。BUT，在對岸的淘寶，事情就不一樣了，有微博網友「裸睡蜀黍」就發現，竟然有個可疑的商品，叫做「一次性包皮環切縫合器」。<br />\n<br />\n難道，這年頭連割包皮手術都得自己來了嗎，這心理壓力也大得太誇張了吧！<br />\n<br />\n再進一步搜尋，就會發現這個東西的設計還真的很不可思議，只要把要切割的包皮固定好，套入這個器具裡，再壓下把手5秒左右讓刀刃密合.....「長袖」就已經變成「短袖」了啊（驚嚇）。<br />\n<br />\n更驚人的是，這個東西還強調它可以同時完成縫合，取下之後只要靜養三天、不用拆線，就可以回復到良好的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n但不管再怎麼方便，這東西如果自己操作，未免還是太危險了，誰知道會發生什麼事？也有淘寶店家寫著「本品為醫療器材，僅出貨給醫療從業人士」，就是不曉得是不是真的會嚴格執行。<br />\n<br />\n總而言之呢，這個東西還是應該要給醫生在手術時使用的， 問答網站「知乎」上，也有網友分享，他到醫院進行手術，醫生就是打完麻醉之後用這個切割。不過他也提到，到醫院總共花了人民幣2500元（約台幣12000元），再看看淘寶上的售價......嗯.....一把人民幣200元（約台幣900元），甚至15元的都有。<br />\n<br />\n可能那些「自助割包皮」的人，就是不怕手術風險跟沒打麻醉，打算硬是咬牙省出個萬把塊吧......。那個情境光想就怕，好孩子千萬不要模仿，記得乖乖去看醫生喔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到段片都覺得係玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wDLz48a37VY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwDLz48a37VY&d=M8G5bui%2BjxuA9%2FsWM%2F8cFtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=df093c65\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wDLz48a37VY</a>"},{"pid":"ff123ddc9a284cabd0457a8dcd8480b0edeb975e","tid":780934,"uid":134683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:49:23.000Z","msg":"最頂癮係呢把尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/214830_23d8fc38f7d4952f359926a39a8bff56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F214830_23d8fc38f7d4952f359926a39a8bff56.png&h=e2e858eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fa2c480d7bd8b85e6fa6b28cfca27fdd92a8db8","tid":780934,"uid":27596,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"我相信只要係男人<br />\n都唔會買嚟自己割<br />\n即使係蠢撚到仆街嘅蝗<br />\n<br />\n都唔會搵自己命根嚟玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849d13c283845f3fcb417ae2695e12f3c1792d8c","tid":780934,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fa2c480d7bd8b85e6fa6b28cfca27fdd92a8db8","tid":780934,"uid":27596,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"我相信只要係男人<br />\n都唔會買嚟自己割<br />\n即使係蠢撚到仆街嘅蝗<br />\n<br />\n都唔會搵自己命根嚟玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:51:56.000Z","msg":"介紹親戚朋友用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfab716fa79a1b5aa1ff25a194266fef12495303","tid":780934,"uid":88723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"理論性可行 <br />\n但實際應該call白車收尾"},{"pid":"980ce5611fe848917798e0968f1ba9ff8b5c15e8","tid":780934,"uid":88396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"切斷重練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3b3abf6a7ca7f0bac8499c8fa2ce172245b167","tid":780934,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:53:39.000Z","msg":"中國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失靈成碌切晒都唔出奇"},{"pid":"4efd54f6cfbea4b8f8ec19a5757266845986d505","tid":780934,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"令我想起一單外國新聞<br />\n夜店相遇，女方醉咗見到男方包皮，就親自動手替佢割，好似最後斷埋call白車。"},{"pid":"870f0839cdbe921f82cf40a7d6570e58cdaf3e37","tid":780934,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"有無人評價？"},{"pid":"f29bef216dc10d2a9912842a179419db2d73e850","tid":780934,"uid":43083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:56:36.000Z","msg":"一邊睇條片   細佬一路赤赤痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f2e6fe85f671bfacb0bcd7d33cc93407bd3488","tid":780934,"uid":114097,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"丁得一條<br />\n切完梗係一次性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be23403cbd47a381b4371c7fecf106359b7f9d6b","tid":780934,"uid":77587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:58:03.000Z","msg":"其實出左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲評價仲有圖 一堆傻閪用完出哂膿"},{"pid":"557f2eb904a025d96da7608804d452eca2cc9293","tid":780934,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"試過幾好用"},{"pid":"d95703170a487e6e48991423d0bcbbff4b3c1231","tid":780934,"uid":27596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:21:34.000Z","msg":"割包皮呢啲小手術其實好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲錢邊可以慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee0af754ac185e9abf144dcf13b1c17cc4dea54","tid":780934,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"557f2eb904a025d96da7608804d452eca2cc9293","tid":780934,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"試過幾好用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=